title: A1369 820-3023-A 3 beeps
message:
Hi,

I have an A1369 820-3023-A that gives 3 beeps, and doesn't boot. For what I've read in foruns, I think that it might be a RAM module or CPU. Is there any way for me to test the RAM modules, to try to figure out witch one is bad?

title: A1369 820-3023-A 3 beeps
message: Waste of time, usually CPU problem.
